    "description": "<strong>This 45-minute gameplay demo will allow you to familiarize yourself with the full game mechanics by adopting 4 unique capybaras in your park. We'll be updating the demo regularly to resolve any bugs or problems you may encounter during gameplay, so don't hesitate to let us know.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/ea1c816cdb66ff33353baa4e13252950.webp?t=1747833294\" width=596 height=10 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Full Game Features</strong></h2>Relax in this peaceful game and take care of your favorite little residents: capybaras! Create menus that meet their needs, keep them happy and grow your park<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enjoy a cozy game</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/ea1c816cdb66ff33353baa4e13252950.webp?t=1747833294\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br>Do as the capybaras do, make yourself comfortable and have a good time. There's no time pressure<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/717b6fab60e55e951160082839de2c2d.poster.avif?t=1747833294\" width=426 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/717b6fab60e55e951160082839de2c2d.webm?t=1747833294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/717b6fab60e55e951160082839de2c2d.mp4?t=1747833294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build and decorate your own park</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/ea1c816cdb66ff33353baa4e13252950.webp?t=1747833294\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br>Design and decorate your capybara's enclosures with care. Unlock new decorative and comfort features to enhance your capybara's well-being.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/d0e0b0b349ead2fa2aabaeae35482962.poster.avif?t=1747833294\" width=426 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/d0e0b0b349ead2fa2aabaeae35482962.webm?t=1747833294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/d0e0b0b349ead2fa2aabaeae35482962.mp4?t=1747833294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Adapt to the specific needs of each capybara</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/ea1c816cdb66ff33353baa4e13252950.webp?t=1747833294\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br>Each capybara has its own needs, grows its own food and carefully chooses the composition of its plate to enhance its well-being with an addictive mini-game inspired by inventory management games.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/7bd1097276353482d63bc1ad09c4c24f.poster.avif?t=1747833294\" width=426 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/7bd1097276353482d63bc1ad09c4c24f.webm?t=1747833294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/7bd1097276353482d63bc1ad09c4c24f.mp4?t=1747833294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Grow your park</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/ea1c816cdb66ff33353baa4e13252950.webp?t=1747833294\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br>Expand your park by adding new enclosures for your capybaras and welcome more visitors.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/3c4e02587047ee4d81479c84bdc72834.poster.avif?t=1747833294\" width=426 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/3c4e02587047ee4d81479c84bdc72834.webm?t=1747833294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/3c4e02587047ee4d81479c84bdc72834.mp4?t=1747833294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
